==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Water hare
<hw>Wa"ter hare</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A small
American hare or rabbit (<spn>Lepus aquaticus</spn>) found on or near
the southern coasts of the United States; -- called also <altname>water
rabbit</altname>, and <altname>swamp hare</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water hemlock</ent>⟦br⟧
